{"lastModified":1761071781485,"uri":"c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: West Mediterranean\n\nHAZE is an 85-foot yacht manufactured by Extra Yachts in 2021. It features a Fiberglass/GRP hull, ensuring durability and low maintenance.\n\nThis yacht is impressive in performance, reaching a maximum speed of 21 knots and comfortably cruising at 12 knots. It incorporates photo-voltaic cells for sustainable energy generation, showcasing an eco-conscious approach to luxury.\n\nWith 86 GT, HAZE offers a spacious layout, accommodating 8 guests in 4 staterooms. The design by Francesco Guida highlights clean exterior lines, while the interior, crafted by Lawson Robb and Francesco Guida, emphasizes panoramic views and thoughtful spaces.\n\nThe main salon is bright, welcoming natural light through panoramic windows and a glazed ceiling. Outside, there's a sizable 50-square-meter beach club with a hydraulic swim platform, along with a flybridge featuring ample seating and sun pads for relaxation. HAZE received recognition for its interior design with the \"Interior Design under 40m\" award, showcasing its exceptional design and functionality.","blueprint":{"name":"HAZE","images":["/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::75e08ad0-cf2a-11ee-9a5d-47df8394c922.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::800ee560-cf2a-11ee-9a5d-47df8394c922.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::800fcfc0-cf2a-11ee-9a5d-47df8394c922.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::800f5a90-cf2a-11ee-9a5d-47df8394c922.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5c986c1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::800e2210-cf2a-11ee-9a5d-47df8394c922.jpeg/{imageVa